<div class="vine-p p-comment_Comment showAvatars commentbody " id="c74392582"><div class="printerData hide" data-printer="{&quot;commentId&quot;:74392582,&quot;authorDomain&quot;:&quot;chrisboese&quot;,&quot;authorDisplayName&quot;:&quot;Chris Boese&quot;}"></div><div class="c_author"><div class="normal"><a href="http://chrisboese.newsvine.com/"><img class="comment_author_avatar" src="http://www.cdn.newsvine.com/_vine/images/_/blank.gif" data-avatar_src="http://m.static.newsvine.com/servista/imagesizer?file=chrisboeseAF00623D-94A0-E429-55B5-A2D37774E86B.jpg&width=60" width="35" height="35" alt="Comment author avatar" data-is_default_avatar="false" /></a><a href="http://chrisboese.newsvine.com/">Chris Boese</a></div></div><div id="commentText_74392582" class="c_text"><div class="normal"><div class="commentSource"><p>Great story, Laura! This is fascinating. </p></div>
<div class="vine-p p-comment_MiniToolbox"><div class="printerData hide" data-printer="{&quot;commentId&quot;:74392582,&quot;threadId&quot;:&quot;3672830&quot;,&quot;contentId&quot;:&quot;17067896&quot;,&quot;authorDomain&quot;:&quot;chrisboese&quot;}"></div><ul class="list"><li class="box votes"><div class="label">1 vote</div></li></ul></div><img class="replybutton" src="http://www.cdn.newsvine.com/_vine/images/_/b_reply_mini.gif" width="35" height="12" alt="Reply" /><span class="commentdate"><a href="#c74392582" title="Link to this comment">#1</a> - Sat Feb 23, 2013 11:09 AM EST</span><div class="clearfix"></div><div class="commentcontainer"><span></span></div></div></div></div><div class="vine-p p-comment_Comment showAvatars commentbody " id="c74393725"><div class="printerData hide" data-printer="{&quot;commentId&quot;:74393725,&quot;authorDomain&quot;:&quot;nelsonouellet&quot;,&quot;authorDisplayName&quot;:&quot;Nelson Ouellet&quot;}"></div><div class="c_author"><div class="normal"><a href="http://nelsonouellet.newsvine.com/"><img class="comment_author_avatar" src="http://www.cdn.newsvine.com/_vine/images/_/blank.gif" data-avatar_src="http://www.cdn.newsvine.com/_vine/images/av/60x60/msnbc.jpg" width="35" height="35" alt="Comment author avatar" data-is_default_avatar="true" /></a><a href="http://nelsonouellet.newsvine.com/">Nelson Ouellet</a></div></div><div id="commentText_74393725" class="c_text"><div class="normal"><div class="commentSource"><p>Obviously, someone messep up somewhere in Mississippi. But what about someone or some people higher up in Congress? After the 1995 ratification, should Congress then have been insisting that Mississippi help complete the certification? And what about the press and the U.S. population? Stange indeed that this one slipped between the cracks for so long... twice!</p></div><div class="vine-p p-comment_MiniToolbox"><div class="printerData hide" data-printer="{&quot;commentId&quot;:74393725,&quot;threadId&quot;:&quot;3672830&quot;,&quot;contentId&quot;:&quot;17067896&quot;,&quot;authorDomain&quot;:&quot;nelsonouellet&quot;}"></div><ul class="list"><li class="box votes"><div class="label">1 vote</div></li></ul></div><img class="replybutton" src="http://www.cdn.newsvine.com/_vine/images/_/b_reply_mini.gif" width="35" height="12" alt="Reply" /><span class="commentdate"><a href="#c74393725" title="Link to this comment">#2</a> - Sat Feb 23, 2013 12:09 PM EST</span><div class="vine-p p-comment_Comment showAvatars commentbody child " id="c74393836"><div class="printerData hide" data-printer="{&quot;commentId&quot;:74393836,&quot;authorDomain&quot;:&quot;laura-conaway&quot;,&quot;authorDisplayName&quot;:&quot;Laura Conaway&quot;}"></div><div class="c_author"><div class="normal"><a href="http://laura-conaway.newsvine.com/"><img class="comment_author_avatar" src="http://www.cdn.newsvine.com/_vine/images/_/blank.gif" data-avatar_src="http://m.static.newsvine.com/servista/imagesizer?file=laura-conaway383A3E4D-A0F7-2BEC-FAC3-636E2F28B278.jpg&width=60" width="35" height="35" alt="Comment author avatar" data-is_default_avatar="false" /></a><a href="http://laura-conaway.newsvine.com/">Laura Conaway</a></div></div><div id="commentText_74393836" class="c_text"><div class="normal"><div class="commentSource"><p>@Nelson, that's an interesting way to look at it. I have to go back through the history more and see what, if any, response the news of Mississippi's 1995 got in Washington, D.C.</p></div><div class="vine-p p-comment_MiniToolbox"><div class="printerData hide" data-printer="{&quot;commentId&quot;:74393836,&quot;threadId&quot;:&quot;3672830&quot;,&quot;contentId&quot;:&quot;17067896&quot;,&quot;authorDomain&quot;:&quot;laura-conaway&quot;}"></div><ul class="list"><li class="box votes"><div class="label">1 vote</div></li></ul></div><span class="commentdate"><a href="#c74393836" title="Link to this comment">#2.1</a> - Sat Feb 23, 2013 12:15 PM EST</span></div></div></div><div class="clearfix"><img class="replybutton" src="http://www.cdn.newsvine.com/_vine/images/_/b_reply_mini.gif" width="35" height="12" alt="Reply" /></div><div class="commentcontainer"><span></span></div></div></div></div><div class="vine-p p-comment_Comment showAvatars commentbody " id="c74396301"><div class="printerData hide" data-printer="{&quot;commentId&quot;:74396301,&quot;authorDomain&quot;:&quot;fb-paulsc2&quot;,&quot;authorDisplayName&quot;:&quot;Paul S. Campbell&quot;}"></div><div class="c_author"><div class="normal"><a href="http://fb-paulsc2.newsvine.com/"><img class="comment_author_avatar" src="http://www.cdn.newsvine.com/_vine/images/_/blank.gif" data-avatar_src="http://m.static.newsvine.com/servista/imagesizer?file=fb-paulsc22A1B2BE7-7D1A-0DDB-5307-F706759E0B19.jpg&width=60" width="35" height="35" alt="Comment author avatar" data-is_default_avatar="false" /></a><a href="http://fb-paulsc2.newsvine.com/">Paul S. Campbell</a></div></div><div id="commentText_74396301" class="c_text"><div class="normal"><div class="commentSource"><p>So tell me, are they now going to enforce the law and free all those slaves working the night shift in the casino?</p></div><div class="vine-p p-comment_MiniToolbox"><div class="printerData hide" data-printer="{&quot;commentId&quot;:74396301,&quot;threadId&quot;:&quot;3672830&quot;,&quot;contentId&quot;:&quot;17067896&quot;,&quot;authorDomain&quot;:&quot;fb-paulsc2&quot;}"></div><ul class="list"></ul></div><img class="replybutton" src="http://www.cdn.newsvine.com/_vine/images/_/b_reply_mini.gif" width="35" height="12" alt="Reply" /><span class="commentdate"><a href="#c74396301" title="Link to this comment">#3</a> - Sat Feb 23, 2013 2:35 PM EST</span><div class="clearfix"></div><div class="commentcontainer"><span></span></div></div></div></div><div class="vine-p p-comment_Comment showAvatars commentbody " id="c74401894"><div class="printerData hide" data-printer="{&quot;commentId&quot;:74401894,&quot;authorDomain&quot;:&quot;dofg&quot;,&quot;authorDisplayName&quot;:&quot;DofG&quot;}"></div><div class="c_author"><div class="normal"><a href="http://dofg.newsvine.com/"><img class="comment_author_avatar" src="http://www.cdn.newsvine.com/_vine/images/_/blank.gif" data-avatar_src="http://www.cdn.newsvine.com/_vine/images/av/60x60/msnbc.jpg" width="35" height="35" alt="Comment author avatar" data-is_default_avatar="true" /></a><a href="http://dofg.newsvine.com/">DofG</a></div></div><div id="commentText_74401894" class="c_text"><div class="normal"><div class="commentSource"><p>This kind of story is a good relativistic anecdote to the greater story, or question, of why racism truly exist, which no one, especially in mainstream media, is willing to answer.</p>
<p>"Black folks don't have a problem. White folks got a problem!....Black folks problem is that white folks got a problem"! That problem is white supremacy. -- Opening line from "Hidden Colors II"</p></div><div class="vine-p p-comment_MiniToolbox"><div class="printerData hide" data-printer="{&quot;commentId&quot;:74401894,&quot;threadId&quot;:&quot;3672830&quot;,&quot;contentId&quot;:&quot;17067896&quot;,&quot;authorDomain&quot;:&quot;dofg&quot;}"></div><ul class="list"><li class="box votes"><div class="label">1 vote</div></li></ul></div><img class="replybutton" src="http://www.cdn.newsvine.com/_vine/images/_/b_reply_mini.gif" width="35" height="12" alt="Reply" /><span class="commentdate"><a href="#c74401894" title="Link to this comment">#4</a> - Sun Feb 24, 2013 12:07 AM EST</span><div class="vine-p p-comment_Comment showAvatars commentbody child " id="c74403282"><div class="printerData hide" data-printer="{&quot;commentId&quot;:74403282,&quot;authorDomain&quot;:&quot;fb-paulsc2&quot;,&quot;authorDisplayName&quot;:&quot;Paul S. Campbell&quot;}"></div><div class="c_author"><div class="normal"><a href="http://fb-paulsc2.newsvine.com/"><img class="comment_author_avatar" src="http://www.cdn.newsvine.com/_vine/images/_/blank.gif" data-avatar_src="http://m.static.newsvine.com/servista/imagesizer?file=fb-paulsc22A1B2BE7-7D1A-0DDB-5307-F706759E0B19.jpg&width=60" width="35" height="35" alt="Comment author avatar" data-is_default_avatar="false" /></a><a href="http://fb-paulsc2.newsvine.com/">Paul S. Campbell</a></div></div><div id="commentText_74403282" class="c_text"><div class="normal"><div class="commentSource"><p>Racism,religious differences,and all the other crap that causes jock itch is derived from a need to feel superior i.e. making God in our image, Calling Muslims heathens, laying claim to knowledge that we stole from other civilizations and going to war over straight versus gay(I know its not a versus situation but do they?)</p>
<p>To expect low flying birds to overcome the peaks is asking a lot. So we pardon them their ignorance as we admire our own intellect and compassion.</p></div><div class="vine-p p-comment_MiniToolbox"><div class="printerData hide" data-printer="{&quot;commentId&quot;:74403282,&quot;threadId&quot;:&quot;3672830&quot;,&quot;contentId&quot;:&quot;17067896&quot;,&quot;authorDomain&quot;:&quot;fb-paulsc2&quot;}"></div><ul class="list"><li class="box votes"><div class="label">2 votes</div></li></ul></div><span class="commentdate"><a href="#c74403282" title="Link to this comment">#4.1</a> - Sun Feb 24, 2013 7:41 AM EST</span></div></div></div><div class="clearfix"><img class="replybutton" src="http://www.cdn.newsvine.com/_vine/images/_/b_reply_mini.gif" width="35" height="12" alt="Reply" /></div><div class="commentcontainer"><span></span></div></div></div></div><div class="vine-p p-comment_Comment showAvatars commentbody " id="c74406222"><div class="printerData hide" data-printer="{&quot;commentId&quot;:74406222,&quot;authorDomain&quot;:&quot;sandyc954&quot;,&quot;authorDisplayName&quot;:&quot;sandyc954&quot;}"></div><div class="c_author"><div class="normal"><a href="http://sandyc954.newsvine.com/"><img class="comment_author_avatar" src="http://www.cdn.newsvine.com/_vine/images/_/blank.gif" data-avatar_src="http://m.static.newsvine.com/servista/imagesizer?file=sandyc954508CABD8-29C5-8E38-4000-6320D55A0014.jpg&width=60" width="35" height="35" alt="Comment author avatar" data-is_default_avatar="false" /></a><a href="http://sandyc954.newsvine.com/">sandyc954</a></div></div><div id="commentText_74406222" class="c_text"><div class="normal"><div class="commentSource"><p>People still hiding their crimes and get things their own way, regardless of the advancements made toward equality.</p>
<p>Racial equality is still debated, but it should not take so long. We know people still feel privilege and superior, but the law is not behind them.</p>
<p>They try to keep things unbalanced in their favor, but laws are supposed to be equal for all. Race is the most glaring. Authoritarians trying to keep it.</p>
<p>We should not have had any of these road blocks. We still have the issues and people trying to deny and protect their privilege.</p>
<p>There are still people trying to block this kind of progress. I applaud the progress, but it took how long to get this far? People are still trying to get up that mountain.</p></div><div class="vine-p p-comment_MiniToolbox"><div class="printerData hide" data-printer="{&quot;commentId&quot;:74406222,&quot;threadId&quot;:&quot;3672830&quot;,&quot;contentId&quot;:&quot;17067896&quot;,&quot;authorDomain&quot;:&quot;sandyc954&quot;}"></div><ul class="list"><li class="box votes"><div class="label">1 vote</div></li></ul></div><img class="replybutton" src="http://www.cdn.newsvine.com/_vine/images/_/b_reply_mini.gif" width="35" height="12" alt="Reply" /><span class="commentdate"><a href="#c74406222" title="Link to this comment">#5</a> - Sun Feb 24, 2013 12:33 PM EST</span><div class="clearfix"></div><div class="commentcontainer"><span></span></div></div></div></div><div class="vine-p p-comment_Comment showAvatars commentbody " id="c74406427"><div class="printerData hide" data-printer="{&quot;commentId&quot;:74406427,&quot;authorDomain&quot;:&quot;alvagoldbook&quot;,&quot;authorDisplayName&quot;:&quot;Alva Goldbook&quot;}"></div><div class="c_author"><div class="normal"><a href="http://alvagoldbook.newsvine.com/"><img class="comment_author_avatar" src="http://www.cdn.newsvine.com/_vine/images/_/blank.gif" data-avatar_src="http://m.static.newsvine.com/servista/imagesizer?file=AlvaGoldbookEAE1F8E9-2BA5-3E0F-3943-B91C9411CDEB.jpg&width=60" width="35" height="35" alt="Comment author avatar" data-is_default_avatar="false" /></a><a href="http://alvagoldbook.newsvine.com/">Alva Goldbook</a></div></div><div id="commentText_74406427" class="c_text"><div class="normal"><div class="commentSource"><p>Wait a second. Does this mean that the paperwork for the State of Mississippi to ratify the 13th Amendment of the United States was <strong><em>lost in the mail?!?!?</em></strong></p>
<p>Next time, hire a courier!</p></div><div class="vine-p p-comment_MiniToolbox"><div class="printerData hide" data-printer="{&quot;commentId&quot;:74406427,&quot;threadId&quot;:&quot;3672830&quot;,&quot;contentId&quot;:&quot;17067896&quot;,&quot;authorDomain&quot;:&quot;alvagoldbook&quot;}"></div><ul class="list"></ul></div><img class="replybutton" src="http://www.cdn.newsvine.com/_vine/images/_/b_reply_mini.gif" width="35" height="12" alt="Reply" /><span class="commentdate"><a href="#c74406427" title="Link to this comment">#6</a> - Sun Feb 24, 2013 12:46 PM EST</span><div class="clearfix"></div><div class="commentcontainer"><span></span></div></div></div></div></div><div class="commentcontainer"><div class="vine-p p-comment_CommentForm commentfields use_zinger"><div class="printerData hide" data-printer="{&quot;canLink&quot;:true,&quot;threadId&quot;:&quot;3672830&quot;,&quot;isPrivate&quot;:false}"></div><a name="entercomment"></a><div class="commentbody"><div class="c_author"><div class="user"><a><img class="comment_author_avatar" src="http://www.cdn.newsvine.com/_vine/images/_/blank.gif" data-avatar_src="http://www.cdn.newsvine.com/_vine/images/av/60x60/msnbc.jpg" width="35" height="35" alt="Author avatar" data-is_default_avatar="true" />Leave a Comment:</a></div></div><div class="c_text"><div class="user"><div class="commentsForm-errors hide"></div><table class="commentform"><tr><td><div class="commentRegFormDiv"><form class="commentRegForm" method="POST" action="/_nv/api/accounts/register"><input type="hidden" name="responseType" value="json"><input type="hidden" name="postCommentGroupJoin" value=""><input type="hidden" name="postCommentGroupAccept" value=""><input type="hidden" name="affiliate" value="msnbc.msn.com"><input type="hidden" name="mailTemplate" value="maddowblog.NewUser"><table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0"><tr><td><label for="commentName">Name: </label></td><td><input type="text" id="commentName" name="displayName" class="half flat"